    "By utilizing the code carbon emissions formula, we can observe that EfficientNetV2M and ResNet50 consume more hardware resources.",
    "The MobileNet has lowest carbon emission while developing model and deploying model shown in Figure 5.",
    "The accuracy of the model for EfficientNetV2M, EfficientNetV2S, ResNet50 and ResNet101 increase as it trains longer; whereas, the accuracy doesn't increase for MobileNet after 12 epochs shown in Figure 6 (a).",
